description:
This is a 13 minute workout called '13 min. Full Body Stretch Routine For Tight Muscles| Beginner Friendly' from the channel Toni Mitchell.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Build Muscle & Sculpt Your Body with my Full Body Workout Guides:
↪︎ https://tonimitchell.com/


Relax with me during this full body stretch routine while loosening up tight muscles. This stretch session is great for flexibility and mobility. No equipment needed.
